Package grafioschtrader.gtnet.model.msg

Class HistoryquoteExchangeMsg

java.lang.Object
grafioschtrader.gtnet.model.msg.HistoryquoteExchangeMsg
public class HistoryquoteExchangeMsg extends Object
Payload for historical price exchange messages (GT_NET_HISTORYQUOTE_EXCHANGE_SEL_C, GT_NET_HISTORYQUOTE_PUSH_SEL_C). In a request: - Contains instruments with date ranges to query - fromDate/toDate specify the requested historical data range - records list is empty (only requesting data) In a response: - Contains instruments with their historical price records - Each instrument's records list contains the actual OHLCV data - Only dates within the requested range that the provider has are included
